channel.title: Goodbye RSC Development
channel.description:
It's been fun while it lasted, but I'm moving on to bigger and better things. Please do not message me regarding RSC Private Servers or RSC Development.
As my last words, I would like to say that I think this community can come back on its feet, so long as some people with real knowledge start cranking out real development. xEnt, Vrunk, Empheral, and many others have proven that this community is worth something, even in it's lack of development at this point.
With graduation a few months away, and work kicking up, I shall leave you all to take what has been passed down to you, and push the limits of what we've seen. I know that has always been my goal in this community was to do what no one else has done, and it worked out pretty well.
Take care all!
